        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p>Cybersecurity Threats Rise In India’s Logistics Industry</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p class="fs-italic">
            “Cybersecurity in logistics has become a pressing concern as supply
            chains increasingly face sophisticated cyber threats. Sensitive
            data, such as consumer information and consignment details, must be
            protected through robust security measures, whether stored on
